      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DAINTREE DAZZLER (2) used the inside draw to advantage last time and hit the ground running with a fast early split, paving the way for a head win at this track over 350m in 19.41. Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Can continue on his winning ways. MAN OF COURAGE (8) was in winning form two back (22.14) at Warrnambool but ran below best last time at Ballarat, finishing 7th. The form out of last race has been strong. Has ability and can measure up. WALTER WALRUS (5) has a strong record this track and trip with four wins and two placings from nine starts. Missed the frame latest (25.84) when fifth over 450m at Shepparton in a Grade 5. With even luck and a clean start can sneak into the finish. HOLLYWOOD FRANKY (1) was in the money last start at big odds - poses a threat again.",
